{"parse":{"title":"Broad Left","pageid":4344652,"revid":773121804,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">For the trade union coalition, see <a href=\"/wiki/Broad_left\" title=\"Broad left\">Broad left</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-content ambox-Unreferenced\" role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"mbox-image\"><div style=\"width:52px\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Question_book-new.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"39\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/75px-Question_book-new.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/100px-Question_book-new.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"512\" data-file-height=\"399\" /></a></div></td><td class=\"mbox-text\"><div class=\"mbox-text-span\">This article <b>does not <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Citing_sources\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citing sources\">cite</a> any <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability\" title=\"Wikipedia:Verifiability\">sources</a></b>.<span class=\"hide-when-compact\"> Please help <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Broad_Left&amp;action=edit\">improve this article</a> by <a href=\"/wiki/Help:Introduction_to_referencing_with_Wiki_Markup/1\" title=\"Help:Introduction to referencing with Wiki Markup/1\">adding citations to reliable sources</a>. Unsourced material may be challenged and <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability#Burden_of_evidence\" title=\"Wikipedia:Verifiability\">removed</a>.</span>  <small><i>(December 2009)</i></small><small class=\"hide-when-compact\"><i> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal\" title=\"Help:Maintenance template removal\">Learn how and when to remove this template message</a>)</i></small></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Broad Left</b> was a political faction within the <a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\">National Union of Students of the United Kingdom</a> (NUS) during the 1970s. It consisted of a working relationship between the <a href=\"/wiki/Labour_Party_(UK)\" title=\"Labour Party (UK)\">Labour Party</a>, the <a href=\"/wiki/Liberal_Party_(UK)\" title=\"Liberal Party (UK)\">Liberal Party</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Plaid_Cymru\" title=\"Plaid Cymru\">Plaid Cymru</a>, the <a href=\"/wiki/Communist_Party_of_Great_Britain\" title=\"Communist Party of Great Britain\">Communist Party of Great Britain</a> (CPGB), and other, non-aligned, supporters in order to work as a single voting bloc against the <a href=\"/wiki/Conservative_Party_(UK)\" title=\"Conservative Party (UK)\">Conservative</a> and some <a href=\"/wiki/Trotskyist\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Trotskyist\">Trotskyist</a> student groups. It held the union presidency from 1973 to 1982.\n</p><p>The Broad Left movement should not be confused with the <a href=\"/wiki/Student_Broad_Left\" title=\"Student Broad Left\">Student Broad Left</a> movement, also an NUS faction.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notable_members\">Notable members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Broad_Left&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Notable members\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Those elected to the NUS executive on the Broad Left ticket include the following:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/David_Aaronovitch\" title=\"David Aaronovitch\">David Aaronovitch</a> (CPGB; NUS President, 1980-82)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Charles_Clarke\" title=\"Charles Clarke\">Charles Clarke</a> (Labour; NUS President, 1975-77)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Trevor_Phillips\" title=\"Trevor Phillips\">Trevor Phillips</a> (Non-aligned Broad Left; NUS President, 1978-80)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sue_Slipman\" title=\"Sue Slipman\">Sue Slipman</a> (CPGB; NUS President, 1977-78)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Andrew_Lansley\" title=\"Andrew Lansley\">Andrew Lansley</a> (President of the Guild of Students)<sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\"><span title=\"This claim needs references to reliable sources. (November 2016)\">citation needed</span></a></i>&#93;</sup></li></ul>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"Template:National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"Template talk:National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\"><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\">National Union of Students (United Kingdom)</a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Presidents</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Shakira_Martin_(NUS)\" title=\"Shakira Martin (NUS)\">Shakira Martin</a> (2017-19)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Presidents_of_the_National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"List of Presidents of the National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\">List of Presidents</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Structure</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_LGBT_Campaign\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"National Union of Students LGBT Campaign\">LGBT</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_Disabled_Students%27_Campaign\" title=\"National Union of Students Disabled Students&#39; Campaign\">Disabled</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_Black_Students%27_Campaign\" title=\"National Union of Students Black Students&#39; Campaign\">Black</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_Women%27s_Campaign\" title=\"National Union of Students Women&#39;s Campaign\">Women</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_Scotland\" title=\"National Union of Students Scotland\">Scotland</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students-Union_of_Students_in_Ireland\" title=\"National Union of Students-Union of Students in Ireland\">Northern Ireland</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Union_of_Students_Wales\" title=\"National Union of Students Wales\">Wales</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Governance_of_the_National_Union_of_Students_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"Governance of the National Union of Students (United Kingdom)\">Governance </a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Members</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_disaffiliated_Students%27_Unions_in_the_United_Kingdom\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"List of disaffiliated Students&#39; Unions in the United Kingdom\">Non-affiliated unions</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Groupings</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Labour_Students\" title=\"Labour Students\">Labour Students (NOLS)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/National_Campaign_Against_Fees_and_Cuts\" title=\"National Campaign Against Fees and Cuts\">NCAFC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Workers%27_Student_Society\" title=\"Socialist Workers&#39; Student Society\">SWSS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Student_Broad_Left\" title=\"Student Broad Left\">Student Broad Left</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Organised_Independents\" title=\"Organised Independents\">Organised Independents</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Young_Liberals_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"Young Liberals (United Kingdom)\">Young Liberals</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Conservative_Future\" title=\"Conservative Future\">Conservative Future</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Young_Greens_of_England_and_Wales\" title=\"Young Greens of England and Wales\">Young Greens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Young_Independence\" title=\"Young Independence\">Young Independence (UKIP)</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/ae/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg/30px-Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/ae/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg/45px-Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/ae/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg/60px-Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1200\" data-file-height=\"600\" /></a></td><td><i>This article related to the <a href=\"/wiki/Politics_of_the_United_Kingdom\" title=\"Politics of the United Kingdom\">politics of the United Kingdom</a>, or its predecessor or constituent states, is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Broad_Left&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:UK-poli-stub\" title=\"Template:UK-poli-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:UK-poli-stub\" title=\"Template talk:UK-poli-stub\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:UK-poli-stub&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2257\nCached time: 20180915095508\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage